> add a conclusion that offers suggestions for how protocols should
> protect association and assembly.
>=20
> > Or does Association-00 intend to propose abandoning the framework
> > established with RFC8280? I suppose that too could be a reasoned way to
> > proceed, but I do not see that argument in the current draft either.
